elements.name: Como usuario lector intento filtrar con un tag privado y no puedo

steps.name: I wait for a signal containing "logged" for 30 seconds
I wait for a signal containing "creating tag" for 30 seconds
I wait for a signal containing "tag created" for 30 seconds
I wait for a signal containing "creating post" for 30 seconds
I wait for a signal containing "posting" for 30 seconds
I wait for a signal containing "post created" for 30 seconds
I select the post with title "$$name_2"
I check the tag "$$name_1" does not exist

name: Crear un tag interno y asignarlo a un nuevo post, y verificar que un lector no lo puede ver al entrar al post
